		<node ID="ID_1344702142" TEXT="Machine Structure#$D$#">
		<node ID="ID_1921323556" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine" TEXT="Machine - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_1170930864" TEXT="A machine (or mechanical device) is a mechanical structure that uses power to apply forces and control movement to perform an intended action. Machines can be driven by animals and people by natural forces such as wind and water and by chemical thermal or electrical power and include a system of mechanisms that shape the actuator input to achieve a specific application of output forces " />
