			<node ID="ID_934956767" TEXT="A callback function is one that should be called when a certain condition is met. Instead of being called immediately the callback function is called at a certain point in the future. Typically it is used when a task is being started that will finish asynchronously (ie will finish some time after the calling function has returned)." />
			</node>
