			<node ID="ID_389106477" TEXT="A callback function is essentially a pattern (an established solution to a common problem) and therefore the use of a callback function is also known as a callback pattern. Consider this common use of a callback function in jQuery: //Note that the item in the click methods parameter is a function not a variable." />
