			<node ID="ID_368657312" TEXT="Process management is a series of techniques skills tools and methods used to control and manage a business process within a large system or organization. The term is most commonly used in business analysis productivity studies and systems engineering.The purpose of process management is to clearly identify and document all the steps and actions taken to complete a process or work flow." />
