			<node ID="ID_1697947904" TEXT="Scheduling Provides Time of CPU to the Each Process. There are Two Types of Scheduling . 1) Preemptive: In this all the Processes are executed by using some Amount of Time of CPU. The Time of CPU is divided into the Number of Minutes and Time of CPU divided into the Process by using Some Rules. if the time is divided into equal interval than it " />
