			<node ID="ID_382400346" TEXT="Segmentation with Paging#$D$#">
		<node ID="ID_124840181" LINK="https://www.javatpoint.com/os-segmented-paging" TEXT="OS Segmented Paging - javatpoint">
			<node ID="ID_366424513" TEXT="Segmented Paging. Pure segmentation is not very popular and not being used in many of the operating systems. However Segmentation can be combined with Paging to get the best features out of both the techniques. In Segmented Paging the main memory is divided into variable size segments which are further divided into fixed size pages." />
